1213
01:28:05.054 --> 01:28:09.125
Right. That's okay.
Sure.


1214
01:28:09.158 --> 01:28:12.061
Uh, Liz, did Harry call?

1215
01:28:16.866 --> 01:28:20.069
Okay. You know
where to reach me, huh?


1216
01:28:24.073 --> 01:28:28.077
I'm sorry. It was a busy weekend,
and I had to leave a number.


1217
01:28:28.111 --> 01:28:32.982
Does Harry know you're here? No.
