1223
01:28:50.533 --> 01:28:56.039
but, uh, now I'm getting
definite negative feedback.


1224
01:28:56.072 --> 01:28:58.141
When did you go into analysis?

1225
01:28:58.174 --> 01:29:02.445
- How did you know I was in analysis?
- Just a wild guess.


1226
01:29:02.478 --> 01:29:05.882
What made you start?

1227
01:29:05.915 --> 01:29:10.219
My value system changed. One day,
I took a look at my $150,000 house...


1228
01:29:10.253 --> 01:29:15.925
and the three cars in the garage and
the swimming pool and the gardeners,


1229
01:29:15.959 --> 01:29:19.195
and I asked myself, "Why?"

1230
01:29:19.228 --> 01:29:23.166
I mean, did I really
want the whole status trip?


1231
01:29:23.199 --> 01:29:27.871
So I decided to try to find out
what I did want and who I was.


1232
01:29:27.904 --> 01:29:31.207
So you went from analysis
to Esalen to Gestalt...


1233
01:29:31.240 --> 01:29:35.611
to encounter groups to
transactional to nirvana, huh?


1234
01:29:35.644 --> 01:29:39.248
Just because some people are trying
to widen their emotional horizons...


1235
01:29:39.282 --> 01:29:41.851
doesn't make the experience
any less valid.


1236
01:29:41.885 --> 01:29:44.253
I've learned a lot.
So I've noticed.


1237
01:29:44.287 --> 01:29:48.257
For one thing, you've learned to talk as
though you're reasoning with somebody...


1238
01:29:48.291 --> 01:29:51.260
about to jump from a high ledge.

1239
01:29:51.294 --> 01:29:56.032
Okay, okay. I know sometimes I tend
to overcompensate for my emotionalism.


1240
01:29:58.134 --> 01:30:01.971
Occasionally, there's a loss of
spontaneity. I'm working on that.


1241
01:30:02.005 --> 01:30:06.142
Well, I'm glad to hear it.
What else have you learned?


1242
01:30:08.177 --> 01:30:11.614
That behind the walls
I've built around myself,


1243
01:30:11.647 --> 01:30:15.384
I'm a warm, caring,
loving human being.


1244
01:30:15.418 --> 01:30:19.088
Well, I could've
told you that 20 years ago.


1245
01:30:21.090 --> 01:30:25.261
Tell me. How's Helen reacting to
