01:31:14.310 --> 01:31:18.514
No. No.
Tell 'em that's our final offer.


1257
01:31:18.547 --> 01:31:21.284
Oh, that's a lot of bull.
I know it's a good piece of property,


1258
01:31:21.317 --> 01:31:25.254
but he needs us
more than we need him.


1259
01:31:25.288 --> 01:31:29.692
Well, if he doesn't like it, tell him
to shove it. And don't worry. He won't.


1260
01:31:31.627 --> 01:31:35.564
Okay, hon. Thanks.
Anything else?


1261
01:31:35.598 --> 01:31:38.734
All right. Well,
I'll be at this number.


1262
01:31:38.767 --> 01:31:41.170
Okay.

1263
01:31:42.305 --> 01:31:45.975
I'm buying another store.
