01:33:02.185 --> 01:33:05.521
No. In many ways,
I've never felt closer to you.


1285
01:33:05.554 --> 01:33:11.427
I don't know. Somehow it seems
to me our lives are out of synch.


1286
01:33:11.460 --> 01:33:15.664
Look. We all realize our potential
in different ways at different times.


1287
01:33:15.698 --> 01:33:19.202
The important thing is, does what you
do give you a sense of fulfillment?


1288
01:33:19.235 --> 01:33:23.106
Well, I'm working on it.
And you have everything you want?


1289
01:33:23.139 --> 01:33:26.075
With one minor exception.

1290
01:33:26.109 --> 01:33:30.846
Somewhere along the way,
I seem to have lost my husband.


1291
01:33:30.879 --> 01:33:35.384
- Lost him?
- Well, I don't know if I lost him...


1292
01:33:35.418 --> 01:33:37.720
