1293
01:33:37.753 --> 01:33:42.225
He left home four days ago,
and I haven't heard from him since.


1294
01:33:42.258 --> 01:33:46.629
How do you feel about that?
George, do me a favor.


1295
01:33:46.662 --> 01:33:50.158
Stop talking as though you're
leading a human potential group.


1296
01:33:50.183 --> 01:33:51.767
It really pisses me off.

