1315
01:35:03.739 --> 01:35:07.876
Okay. I think...
Don't tell me how you think.


1316
01:35:07.910 --> 01:35:11.880
Tell me how you feel.

1317
01:35:11.914 --> 01:35:15.318
Like I've been kicked
in the stomach.


1318
01:35:15.351 --> 01:35:17.520
What else?

1319
01:35:18.921 --> 01:35:24.927
Angry. Hurt. Betrayed.

1320
01:35:24.960 --> 01:35:28.331
And, okay, a little guilty.
But I'll tell you something.


1321
01:35:28.364 --> 01:35:31.434
I really resent the fact that
he's making me feel guilty.


1322
01:35:31.467 --> 01:35:33.869
Why do you feel resentment?

1323
01:35:33.902 --> 01:35:37.973
Well, look. I didn't marry Harry
because he had a good head for business.


1324
01:35:38.006 --> 01:35:42.345
Okay. So it turns out that I do,
or maybe I was lucky. I don't know.


1325
01:35:42.378 --> 01:35:48.284
The point is, I don't love him any less
just 'cause he's a failure as a provider,


1326
01:35:48.317 --> 01:35:52.855
so why should he love me less
just 'cause I'm a success?


1327
01:35:52.888 --> 01:35:55.758
Have you told him you still love him?
Love him.


1328
01:35:57.593 --> 01:36:01.397
What's he think I've been
hanging around for 27 years for?


1329
01:36:01.430 --> 01:36:04.933
Would it be so hard to let him
know you understand how he feels?


1330
01:36:04.967 --> 01:36:07.836
Right now it would, yes.

1331
01:36:07.870 --> 01:36:10.373
Do you want him back?

1332
01:36:11.874 --> 01:36:15.344
