I won't have you.


1336
01:36:33.429 --> 01:36:38.301
- I'm always with you in spirit.
- Thanks a lot.


1337
01:36:38.334 --> 01:36:42.671
It's kind of difficult to put your
cold feet on somebody's spirit,


1338
01:36:42.705 --> 01:36:45.741
especially when
they're 400 miles away.


1339
01:36:50.078 --> 01:36:54.883
